snippet.title: Pak Air Force Conducts Military Exercise Fearing India's Attack

localized.description:
Expecting a reprisal strike from India after Uri terror attack, Pakistan seems to be preparing for the worst. The leaves of Pakistan army personal have been cancelled, motor ways and air space have been shut down and the Pak air force conducts constant military drills.
